        "title": "feat: add Helium browser support",
        "body": "Add support for [Helium Browser](https://heliumbrowser.com) (macOS only), a Chromium-based browser with bundle ID `net.imput.helium`.\n\n### Changes\n- Add `BrowserHelium` constant and include in `DefaultBrowsers()`\n- Map Helium to the Chromium-family cookie reader\n- Keychain Safe Storage: `Helium Storage Key` / account `Helium`\n- macOS profile path: `~/Library/Application Support/net.imput.helium`\n- Env override: `GOOKIE_HELIUM_SAFE_STORAGE_PASSWORD`\n- Add darwin/linux/windows path tests\n- Update coverage tests to include Helium\n- Update README and package doc\n\n### Verification\n- `go test ./...` passes\n- End-to-end tested against a real Helium browser profile on macOS; successfully reads and decrypts cookies using the keychain-derived key.",
